::Kaiser::
       He lay flat on his back as he watched the shots pass harmlessly over 
him.  Quickly springing to his feet he stashes his blaster and charges 
pulling two diamond edged scimitars from their sheaths at his sides.  He 
begins an intricate attack pattern of thrusts and slashes at Perceptor, his 
blades a barely visible shimmer as they dance in front of him.

--part1_6f.35263bd5.2b7c68ca_boundary
